Peel Youth Village (PYV) provides transitional housing for youth and support services and programs to the surrounding Acorn community. Supportive Housing Assisted Living (SHAL) provides support to order adults to assist them to age in place. The HIP program is a multidisciplinary team addressing the goal of achieving housing stability and improving quality of life.
